com.itko.lisa.test

Interface NamedType

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    CompanionInterface, DataSet, FilterInterface, MetricIntegration
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Abend, Assertion, CheckResult, CompanionBase, DataSetImpl, FilterBaseImpl, NormalEnd, ReportGenerator, SimpleCompanion, TestNode

    public interface NamedType
    The object's class name is an easy fetch with getClass().getName(), but we often need human usable versions of an object's type that we can use instead. Implement this interface so that editor tools can refer to you by either your class name or a type String. Never, ever change this once you are constructed, because developers will be building mapping lists based on it!
